      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
          "1.  It is narrated from Imam Musa Kadhim (a.s.) who read out from  a  book:  “There  are  lots  of  comforts  for  a  person wearing the Emerald ring and there is no hardship for him.” The narrator wrote down these words of Imam (a.s.)."
        ]
